## Architecture

This project follows **hexagonal (ports & adapters) architecture** inside `src/{{ package_name }}/`:

```
src/{{ package_name }}/
├── asgi.py              # Uvicorn entrypoint
├── settings.py          # Project settings (pydantic-settings)
├── core/
│   ├── asgi.py          # FastAPI app factory (create_app)
│   ├── handlers/        # Exception-to-response mapping
│   └── management/      # Django-style management commands
├── conf/                # Framework-level defaults
├── db/                  # SQLAlchemy engines, sessions, models, migrations
├── dependencies/        # DI providers (get_db, etc.)
├── domain/              # Pure business logic — zero framework imports
├── services/            # Use-case orchestration
├── repositories/        # Data-access abstraction (port interfaces)
├── middleware/http/      # Per-request DB sessions, exception handling
├── urls/api/v1/         # Route registration (path wiring only)
├── views/               # Request handler logic
├── schemas/             # Pydantic request/response models
├── utils/               # Lifespan hooks, timezone helpers
├── cli/                 # User-facing typer CLI
{% if use_celery %}├── tasks/               # Celery task stubs
{% endif %}└── py.typed             # PEP 561 marker
```

## Quick Start

```bash
# 1. Copy environment variables
cp .env.example .env
# Edit .env with your actual values

# 2. Install dependencies
make install

# 3. Run tests
make test

# 4. Start the development server
make run

# The API is now running at http://localhost:8000
# Interactive docs at http://localhost:8000/docs
```

## Docker

```bash
# Start all services (app + database + Redis)
make docker-up

# Or build the production image manually
make docker-build
```

## Database Migrations

```bash
# Apply all pending migrations
make migrate

# Create a new migration after modifying models
make migration MSG="add users table"
```

## Development Commands

| Command              | Description                                |
|----------------------|--------------------------------------------|
| `make install`       | Install all dependencies via uv            |
| `make lint`          | Run ruff linter                            |
| `make format`        | Auto-format code with ruff                 |
| `make typecheck`     | Run mypy static type analysis              |
| `make test`          | Run full test suite with coverage          |
| `make test-unit`     | Run fast unit tests only (no I/O)          |
| `make test-integration` | Run integration tests (requires DB)     |
| `make run`           | Start dev server with hot-reload           |
| `make docker-build`  | Build production Docker image              |
| `make clean`         | Remove caches and build artifacts          |

