## Pulling Template Updates

This project was generated from the **forge-python-fastapi** Copier template.
To pull in template improvements and new features:

```bash
# From inside this project's root directory
copier update

# Copier will:
#   1. Read your saved answers from .copier-answers.yml
#   2. Pull the latest template version
#   3. Re-render files and show you a diff to review
#   4. Run any _migrations defined for the new version
```

You can also update and re-answer prompts:

```bash
copier update --trust
```

